General.Name: Firebird Metals Ltd
General.Description: Firebird Metals Limited engages in the exploration and evaluation of manganese properties in Australia. Its flagship project is the Oakover Manganese project that includes one granted exploration license and two exploration license applications covering an area of 360 square kilometers located in the Eastern Pilbara Region, Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
